{"tid":674083,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"補習中介仆街","createTime":"2018-05-22T11:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T18:36:19.000Z","uid":36008,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7fd9620f3b3e7bdc74db67c55d17fee29e218054","tid":674083,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"屌 啲補習中介收2星期學費真係好戇鳩<br />\n一星期一堂就收兩堂學費 一星期三堂就收六堂學費<br />\n試過補咗兩堂住港島嘅支那學生補完2堂走撚咗<br />\n個中介仲嚟問我追數<br />\n同啲家長講 咪搵中介 去大學嗰啲學生就業centre嘅網就得<br />\n好似HKU CEDARS/JIJIS咁 分別係HKU/八大學生先入到 唔使俾錢agent賺之餘仲可以大家透過講電話/whatsapp溝通下 大概估到對方態度 係咪一個正常人<br />\n<br />\n記住 補習唔使煩 咪俾錢中介<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/22/193641_4608db1e1532f487bdf861b97ad4e6c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F22%2F193641_4608db1e1532f487bdf861b97ad4e6c0.png&h=76acd531&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/22/193642_fa7f52cac446ef81e234d47edb750ece.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F22%2F193642_fa7f52cac446ef81e234d47edb750ece.png&h=2e7decd0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"860d88121edc6e0136635ba9825a1254b83fdeff","tid":674083,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:45:44.000Z","msg":"補LINK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cedars.hku.hk/careers/employers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cedars.hku.hk%2Fcareers%2Femployers&d=4%2Fonko0djVBA3rAAniKUfp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=218fa5ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cedars.hku.hk/careers/employers</a>"},{"pid":"239cc8678695ecd73ea24793e2adcb726401b404","tid":674083,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:50:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bffe30bf6775fe00a12cdc051828748a801d6e